title: Містер і місіс Малишки
overview: "Mr and Mrs Malyshko is a 16-episode ironic detective story about a married couple, Oleksandr and Maria, who are gentle, attentive and loving parents at home. However, as soon as they step outside their apartment, investigator Oleksandr and lawyer Maria immediately turn into irreconcilable rivals. An uncompromising professional confrontation
